    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and proactive subframe reinforcement. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis maintains factory-spec kinematics, benefiting from a pristine suspension setup and original Sachs damping. Finished in impeccable factory paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle offers a visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
