    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection. The premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, free from any bolster wear or creasing. It has never been smoked in, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. All tech interfaces, from the high-resolution displays to the haptic feedback controls, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history documenting every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, the tires are premium-brand with 90% tread remaining, and the undercarriage is as clean as the roof. This listing includes both original fobs, the factory window sticker, and all owner's manuals. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example of automotive excellence.",
